If anything breaks, 90% of the time it is:

✔ JAR path must be:

META-INF/resources/aikau-xhr-service-widget-demo-share/js/example/

✔ Package must match:

name="example"
location="aikau-xhr-service-widget-demo-share/js/example"

✔ URL must work:

/share/service/com/example/doc-count

⸻

💡 If you STILL get blank page after this

Then the issue is NOT code — it is:

* wrong deployment
* wrong module XML
* wrong Share webscript path
* or JS not being loaded at all

